    <entry>
      <title>温度场重建基准</title>
      <link href="/dataset/p/dataset2-index.html"/>
      <url>/dataset/p/dataset2-index.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>欢迎来到温度场重建数据集（Temperature Field Reconstruction Dataset，TFRD）主页。</p><h1 id="热源系统温度场重建任务"><a href="#热源系统温度场重建任务" class="headerlink" title="热源系统温度场重建任务"></a>热源系统温度场重建任务</h1><blockquote><p>温度场重建数据集面向电子设备热管理模块，解决由有限监测位置温度监控感兴趣位置（PoIs）温度，最终实现电子设备健康实时检测。</p></blockquote><h4 id="One-instance-one-task"><a href="#One-instance-one-task" class="headerlink" title="One instance one task"></a>One instance one task</h4><ul><li>基于点的建模<blockquote><p>学习点坐标到温度值的预测</p></blockquote></li></ul><p><img src="/dataset/images/figure/point.jpg" alt="point"></p><h4 id="One-family-one-task"><a href="#One-family-one-task" class="headerlink" title="One family one task"></a>One family one task</h4><ul><li>基于向量的建模<blockquote><p>学习监测点温度到PoIs温度映射</p></blockquote></li></ul><p><img src="/dataset/images/figure/vector.jpg" alt="vector"></p><ul><li>基于图像的建模<blockquote><p>学习监测点温度到PoIs温度映射（域离散化）</p></blockquote></li></ul><p><img src="/dataset/images/figure/image.jpg" alt="image"></p><ul><li>基于图关系的建模<blockquote><p>学习监测点温度到PoIs温度映射（构建graph关系）</p></blockquote></li></ul><p><img src="/dataset/images/figure/graph.jpg" alt="graph"></p><h1 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h1><div class="card-wrapper"><div class="card-title">引用论文</div><div class="card-content"><pre>@article{gong_tfrd,    Author = {Xiaoqian Chen and Zhiqiang Gong and Xiaoyu Zhao and Weien Zhou and Wen Yao},    Title = {A Machine Learning Modelling Benchmark for Temperature Field Reconstruction of Heat-Source Systems},    Journal = {arXiv preprint arXiv:2108.08298},    Year = {2021}} @article{gong_pirl,    Author = {Zhiqiang Gong and Weien Zhou and Jun Zhang and Wei Peng and Wen Yao},    Title = {Physics-Informed Deep Reversible Regression Model for Temperature Field Reconstruction of Heat-Source Systems},    Journal = {arXiv preprint arXiv:2106.11929},    Year = {2021}}</pre></div></div>]]></content>
      
      
      
