    <entry>
      <title>温度场预测基准</title>
      <link href="/dataset/p/dataset1-index.html"/>
      <url>/dataset/p/dataset1-index.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>欢迎来到热源布局预测数据集(Heat-Source Layout Dataset, HSLD)主页。</p><h1 id="热源布局温度场预测任务"><a href="#热源布局温度场预测任务" class="headerlink" title="热源布局温度场预测任务"></a>热源布局温度场预测任务</h1><blockquote><p>热源布局温度场预测任务是在一个给定边界条件的传热问题中，针对任意变化的热源组件布局，可以无需通过数值仿真计算就实现其整体温度场的快速准确预测，从而为实现温度场性能驱动的热源组件布局优化设计提供高效的代理模型工具。</p></blockquote><p><img src="/dataset/images/prediction/TaskIllustration.png" alt="framework"></p><div class="table-container"><table><thead><tr><th style="text-align:center"><img src="/dataset/images/boundary.png" alt="upload successful"></th><th style="text-align:center"><img src="/dataset/images/layout.png" alt="upload successful"></th><th style="text-align:center"><img src="/dataset/images/field.png" alt="upload successful"></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><strong>给定边界条件的传热问题</strong></td><td style="text-align:center"><strong>热源组件布局方案</strong></td><td style="text-align:center"><strong>对应温度场分布</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></div><ul><li>基于图像的建模<blockquote><p>学习热源布局到温度场的映射关系</p></blockquote></li></ul><p><img src="/dataset/images/prediction/image_mapping.png" alt="image"></p><h1 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h1><div class="card-wrapper"><div class="card-title">引用论文</div><div class="card-content"><pre>@article{chen2021,    Author = {Xianqi Chen and Xiaoyu Zhao and Zhiqiang Gong and Jun Zhang and Weien Zhou and Xiaoqian Chen and Wen Yao},    Title = {A Deep Neural Network Surrogate Modeling Benchmark for Temperature Field Prediction of Heat Source Layout},    Journal = {Science China-Physics, Mechanics & Astronomy},    Year = {2021}}@article{zhao2021,    Author = {Xiaoyu Zhao and Zhiqiang Gong and Jun Zhang and Wen Yao and Xiaoqian Chen},    Title = {A surrogate model with data augmentation and deep transfer learning for temperature field prediction of heat source layout},    Journal = {Structural and Multidisciplinary Optimization},    Year = {2021}}</pre></div></div>]]></content>
      
      
      
